out/
cache/
broadcast/*/*/dry-run/
broadcast/**/run-[0-9]*.json
!broadcast/**/run-latest.json

# E2E-only script: runs against the local anvil-kite docker container,
# never against live Kite testnet. Its run-latest.json (block ≈ 0x0…0x20)
# would mislead readers into thinking the corresponding strategy was
# deployed to chain 2368. Keep it local.
#
# DeployPhase2 + RegisterPhase2Strategies + RegisterPhase2StrategiesVariant3
# *did* land on live Kite testnet (block ≈ 0x14381xx, deployer
# 0xECf5e30F...), so their run-latest.json is checked in alongside Phase 1.
broadcast/RegisterFreshStrategy.s.sol/

# Foundry libs are checked in as submodules; don't ignore.
!lib/
